<div align="center">
<p style="font-size: 50px" align="center">Our <b>Inception</b></p>
<p align="center" style="font-size: 35px">Since our inception in 2022,<br /> we scaled up at a swift pace under the inspiring leadership of our Founder,<br /> Mina Soni and his visionary successors, Bhautik Godhani and Jenish Godhani.</p>
<p align="center" style="font-size: 35px">Today, we offer a diverse portfolio of 17 delightfully fresh, pure and delicious dairy products, prepared using the milk supplied directly to us by 165,000+ dairy farmers. With their exceptional support and that of our 600+ strong team, we seek to gain the trust of countless Indian families and realize our vision to be the most loved dairy brand in India.</p>
</div>
<br />
<div>



