               <p align="center" style="font-size: 50px">Our Dairy Farmers<br /><b style="color: #CC0000">Our Strength</b></p></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="style3">
                
                <p align="center" style="font-size: 35px"><b>We can confidently say that fresh and pure products are not just a choice but everyone’s right, because we enjoy the support of incredible dairy farmers.</b></p>
                <p align="center" style="font-size: 35px">They are our biggest strength – the ones who work tirelessly, day in and day out, to provide quality food to people at large. Having found perfect alignment in what we and the dairy farmers aim for, we strive with a sense of collective commitment towards fulfilling our common goal – Always Fresh and Always Pure Milk & Milk Products for Everyone.</p>
                </td>
            <td>
             <asp:Image ID="Image7" runat="server" ImageUrl="~/img/paragraph image aboutus.png" 
